high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table on your left.
Pick up the knife from the table.
Turn right and go to the green can on the floor.
Cut one of the apples in the can into three pieces.
Put the knife in the can.
Pick up a piece of apple from the can.
Turn around and go to the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge door and put the apple on the second shelf. Close the door and refrigerate the apple for 5 minutes. Open the fridge door and take out the apple. Close the fridge door.
Turn left and go to the microwave on your left.
Open the microwave door and put the apple in. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of apple from a green can in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn left then right and head to the white table in the corner.
Grab the knife from the table.
Turn right and face the green trashcan.
Slice the apple on the left with the knife.
Place the knife in the trashcan.
Grab an apple slice from the trashcan.
Turn around and walk , then walk left to the fridge.
Chill the apple slice in the fridge for 3 seconds.
Head left and face the microwave on the right.
Place the apple slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled apple slice in the microwave.

high_descs: turn left, go to white dining table to the right
pick up knife to the right of lettuce on white table
turn right, go to green bin at end of counter
slice tomato on the back left of green bin
place knife in green bin
pick up tomato slice from green bin
turn around, go to black refrigerator to the right
open refrigerator, place tomato slice on second shelf of refrigerator to the right of blue plate, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up tomato slice from refrigerator, close refrigerator
go to microwave to the left
open microwave, place tomato slice on the left side of plate in microwave, close microwave
anns.task_desc: place chilled tomato slice in microwave
